comment: I don’t like all the terrible, horrific things she has done to JD! She actually accused him of terrible acts of SA, trying to ruin & destroy his life, his life time achievements, his friends his family, everything he has ever worked hard for in his life! This is the act of a narcissistic, psychopath who does not deserve any positive acts of kindness or attention! She needs to be canceled to teach her a lesson that you can’t just lie about honest, decent, hardworking people and then expect to get praised for it! Or in her case “get paid for it or get money for it” She needs to be stopped! At least take her off the Air (TV & News Outlets) she is only causing him & his family more stress & pain! It’s just not fair that she can continue to berate or admonish Johnny, she needs to be canceled! Thank you!
commentable_entity.title: Cancel Amber Heard
commentable_entity.description: It's time for people to take a stand. Amber Heard is a liar, a abuser, a manipulator and a narcissist. It's time to stand up and let Hollywood know if you cast her in a role. We, the people, will not support or view your production. She has lied on stand, produced false evidence, all to try and destroy a man's life. We must cancel Amber Heard.
